{
  "texts": [
    "In our study, we performed our training and tests on 1080 Ti graphic card.",
    "Computational performance will be higher on more advanced graphics cards.",
    "The dental caries lesions that were not evaluated using the gold standard method of histological assessment detected and labeled by the annotators on the radiographic images [76].",
    "The model encountered challenges in accurately predicting teeth positioned at the corners of the bitewing image, as opposed to other teeth.",
    "This could be related to the reduced clarity of these specific teeth and the limited amount of data in the training set."
  ]
}